column2: SELECT TOP # pca.specobjid, emline.z as z_noqso, emline.sigmaStars as emline_vdisp, pca.vdisp_median as pca_vdisp, sp.veldisp as sp_vdisp FROM emissionLinesPort AS emline JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscBC0# AS pca ON emline.specobjid = pca.specobjid JOIN specObj as sp ON emline.specobjid = sp.specobjid
